<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Ma a pi leh pute Eden huon sunga um,
 Dogal a hat ziekin;
 Thihna leh lungkhamna mawhpuon a pawt dawk ui,
 Kahna helo ding chu kap chate ei suoksak.

[V2]
 A khawk ngei, a khawkna zen e maw,
 Tuchan hin le;
 Hehpih kulh sunga um, A suoka um dingin,
 Ei dawha bawl ziekin, henkawl ei buhsak hi!

[V3]
 2. Do dan thiempa Setan galhatpa bawldan hi,
 Ei hawn hethiem leu hing:
 Zawhna Thagau chemzam Pathien Thu hiemtuok in,
 Dogal haw zo dingin thimthu tiemsa ahi.

[V4]
 3. Zie khawvel tuoi nunga hin kei ka len sung hin,
 Ka banin ei kaiin;
 Lungkhamna khuk thima albang ka vaih sung hin,
 Aw Thagau Thiengtho Nangin ei hung pui zelin.</lyrics>
<title>A Khawk Ngei!</title>
<hymn_number>162</hymn_number>
<author>China</author>
</song>